name: Fly Casual
Lore: 'As a smuggler, Han had years of experience at avoiding Imperial detection. He chose the approach to Endor''s moon as the time to pass some of that knowledge on to Chewie.',
Text: 'USED: Cancel Early Warning Network or It''s An Older Code. OR During your deploy phase, deploy one starship (deploy -1) and/or one pilot to a system even without presence or Force icons.LOST: Take one Tydirium or Tantive IV into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.',
